EventItemActionText: This Mayor's Message was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on State and Federal Legislation
EventItemTitle: Communication from the Mayor  -  “AN ACT to amend the vehicle and traffic law, in relation to photo speed violation monitoring systems in school speed zones in the city of New York; to amend chapter 189 of the laws of 2013, amending the vehicle and traffic law and the public officers law relating to establishing in a city with a population of one million people or more a demonstration program implementing speed violation monitoring systems in school zones by means of photo devices, in relation to the effectiveness thereof; and to amend chapter 43 of the laws of 2014, amending the vehicle and traffic law, the public officers law and  the  general municipal  law relating to photo speed violation monitoring systems in school speed zones in the city of New  York, in relation to making technical corrections thereto”.  (S.6046-B/A.7798-B)
EventItemMatterName: Photo speed violation monitoring systems in school speed zones in the city of New York (S.6046-B and A.7798-B)
